snippet.textDisplay: This guy has improved like crazy. 8-10 year back i doubted his singing abilities, even though his tonal quality was mesmerizing. But now he is amazing, He has sung this Qawwali with such devotion and conviction, justifying every emotion and spirituality of it. I don't know but i am noticing from few of his recent performances that he is great with Sufi singing. In GIMA awards when he sang 'Kun faya kun' it was very touching with spirituality. I believe if this guy starts singing Sufi songs, trust me no one can match his emotions and spirituality. Great Job Atif!
